            <a class="opener__topics-link " href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/education">Education</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        The Influential Conservative Group Making it Harder for Idaho Districts to Fix Their Schools
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " >        The Idaho Freedom Foundation has gone beyond the education culture wars by targeting local bond and levy elections, which districts rely on heavily to build and repair schools.
    </h2>

    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
     article-meta-1--left     " data-pp-location="article meta">

