    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/guns">Under the Gun</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/state-active-shooter-training-schools-law-enforcement">
                                    Check Your State: Here Are the Active Shooter Training Requirements for Schools and Law Enforcement
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            No states mandate annual active shooter training for police officers, according to an analysis by ProPublica, The Texas Tribune and FRONTLINE. In comparison, at least 37 states require such training in schools, typically on a yearly basis.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/lexi-churchill">Lexi Churchill</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/lomi-kriel">Lomi Kriel</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-02-08EST06:00">Feb. 8, 5 a.m. CST</time>
        </p>

            </div>
